CountryUnited StatesLanguageEnglish
Private Property is a 2022 American thriller film directed by Chadd Harbold and starring Ashley Benson and Shiloh Fernandez.   It is a remake of the 1960 film of the same title.[2]


Cast[edit]
Ashley Benson as Kathryn Carlyle[2]
Shiloh Fernandez as Ben[2]
Logan Miller[2] as Oates
Frank Whaley[2] as Ed Hogate
Jay Pharoah[2] as Richard
King Orba as The Mechanic
Production[edit]
Filming wrapped in Los Angeles in August 2021.[2]

Release[edit]
The film was had a limited release in theaters and was fully released on demand and digital on May 13, 2022.[3][4]

Reception[edit]
The film received negative reviews. It has a 13% rating on Rotten Tomatoes based on eight reviews.[5]
